&lt;li&gt;The US base salary range for this full-time position is $170,000 - $230,000 annually&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;+ equity + benefits&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Our salary ranges are determined by role, level and location&lt;/li&gt;
